inc of west virginia to provide 294550 chemical suits to be made 
with desert camouflage fabric isratex has supplied the suits to 
the military in the past but in traditional dark green camouflage 
one the same day it awarded that 18 million contract roughly 
61 a suit the pentagon also signed a 22 million agreement with 
