proved its case 
the us supreme courts legal test for an obscenity 
determination asks whether the dominant theme of the artwork 
appeals to prurient interest in sex whether the work is patently 
offensive based on contemporary community standards and whether 
the work lacks serious artistic or political value 
if convicted of both charges barrie could be sentenced to one 
