tanks east of the ural mountains out of the area covered by the 
arms negotiations 
these games are tolerated games as long as the numbers dont 
become wholly unreasonable heisbourg said 
the survey was released a day after the united states and the 
soviet union announced agreement in principle on a major 
conventional arms reduction treaty 
