over arbitrary discrimination 
i feel vindicated plaintiff jeff stolzer said this will 
give these nightclubs something to think about 
either there will be some guidelines that are known to 
everybody or they should just stop all door policies altogether and 
let people in first come first serve 
the mayan opened about six months ago in an old porn theater by 
the same name in a custom more typical of new york clubs than west 
coast nightspots getting in is a seemingly mysterious process 
