i would like to answer today a question that has been put to me 
for many weeks it is the question about whether i will agree to 
run for the office of president of the polish republic if my 
candidacy is put forward 
this is the question i have been thinking about for many hours 
many days and weeks it was even commonly thought that it took too 
long but this is a question that is very difficult for me 
personally and generally personally with regard to the 
circumstances in which i must answer it and generally in view of 
the great responsibility of this office 
the time for an answer has come and today i want to give this 
answer a short one 
following great deliberations and consideration of all 
circumstances i have decided to express approval if my candidacy 
is put forward 
one must move forward one cannot retreat from the path poland 
has chosen and fought for so hard this year one cannot expose it 
to dangers one has to go forward in a better faster and more sure 
way but along this path not a different one 
poland which has a great chance in todays world and in europe 
should take the place that is due to it of a wise country based 
on christian values of a country of people who are tolerant toward 
each other a country that coexists well with all its neighbors 
i want to defend this line and these values and my decision 
stems from these motives i am making it with a total feeling of 
modesty i know there are many who are more worthy of this 
position i am making it because the historical situation has put 
me in such a position 
this is all i can say today about the difficulty of this 
decision about a broader and further program i will talk at some 
other time 
today i only want to pass my best greetings to all of you who 
are listening to me 
