saying it would be worked out in us bankruptcy court in 
kalamazoo 
merchants say theyve been only mildly affected by the shutdown 
so far but they worry about a bleak holiday season and an even 
darker future 
i dont know how long ill be able to last says ac bolin 
who owns a furniture store on main street nobody heres making 
enough to even be thinking about buying furniture 
